<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 A dawtnak in a kan kawltu, zaangfahnak in
 A kan kawltu, Vel ngeihnak in a kan cawi tu,
 Khuaruah a har, ka chimthiam lo, hi tluk tiangin
 A kan dawtu, an chim Vanram hmanh ah, an um lai lo.

[C1]
   A lu cung i hling luchin le, an tuknak vual, Le hma ah cun
   Damnak tling kan hmu cang, Halleluijah
   Lei le Van holh nih a tlinh lo
   Kan cung Pathian a kan dawtnak
   Fa pa Jesuh Khrih ah, cotu kan si.

[V2]
 Mi fim pawl mual, photer ding le, mi rum hna ning
 Zahter dingah, san tlai lo rual, a kan au tu,
 Khuaruah a har, chimthiam a ahar, dawtnak vialte
 Cung i dawtnak, a zangfahnak cu kan, nunnak a si.

[V3]
 Kan sualnak le, palhnak bangin, kan cung ah leh
 Rul siang loin, mi ttha bangin, kan kil vengtu,
 Ni tin kan herh, mi thil vialte, sianglo ngeilo a kan petu
 Bawipa a ttha ttha, sunglawi chin seh.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>A DAWTNAK IN A KAN KAWLTU</title>
</song>